<entry stylesheet="matteroverdrive:info/styles/guide.css">
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">$itemName</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">$itemName可用于将[item name=matter_dust]提纯至[item name=matter_dust_refined]。它能够将分解或重组所产生的[item name=matter_dust]进行再次循环利用。</text>
        <image width="64" height="64" src="guide/matter_recycler_small.png" style="float:left;margin-right:4px"></image>
        <image width="159" height="64" src="guide/matter_recycler_wide.png"></image>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">如何使用</title>
        <creates from="[item name=matter_dust]" to="[item name=matter_dust_refined]"></creates>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">将[item name=matter_dust]放置在输入槽并为$itemName提供能量。你可以将[item name=matter_dust_refined]放置在[item name=decomposer]中将它们分解为[guide name=matter_plasma]。</text>
    </page>
    <page class="padded-page">
        <recipe style="text-align:center"></recipe>
    </page>
</entry>
